<bibRefCitation id="EFE7ECE9FFB9FF9EFAB4F8CCFE51F8B9" author="Galinichev, A. V. &amp; Anufriev, G. A." pageId="1" pageNumber="575" pagination="21 - 28" refId="ref3880" refString="Galinichev, A. V. &amp; Anufriev, G. A. (2012 b) Fauna of leafhoppers (Insecta, Homoptera, Cicadellidae) of &quot; Denezhkin Kamen &quot; Nature Reserve and its environs (Sverdlovsk Oblast). Vestnik Orenburgskogo Gosudarstvennogo Universiteta, 10 (146), 21 - 28. [in Russian]" type="journal article" year="2012">Galinichev &amp; Anufriev, 2012b</bibRefCitation>
